snippet.title: Pokémon Crystal Ultimate 1.0 Overview Trailer
snippet.description:
I hope you enjoy the overview of v.1.0 and the game itself! 

For all of the details, I invite you to join my Discord server: https://discord.gg/XMYBvDA. Although you can find it in my Discord server, feel free to take a look at the documentation here: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1VnC8wWP8CjpresyAZV_YlFcY8oWutHZeUr-RQj8lyCI/edit?usp=sharing
